  <brief_title>Study of Oral MD-0727 Administered to Patients With Primary Hypercholesterolemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, Randomized, Multi-Center, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel-Group, Dose-Range-Finding Study of the Safety and Efficacy of Orally Administered MD-0727 in Patients With Primary Hypercholesterolemia</official_title>
  <sponsors>
