  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objectives of this study are to evaluate the safety of MD-0727 in patients with
      primary hypercholesterolemia and to determine the low density lipoprotein cholesterol (LDL-C)
      lowering effect and dose-response of MD-0727 in patients with primary hypercholesterolemia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
